definitions.definition: (chiefly American) A person without religious affiliation.

main_definition: (chiefly American) A person without religious affiliation.

definitions.definition: Alternative form of nones : the ninth hour after dawn ; ( Christianity ) the religious service appointed to this hour .
Synonym of midafternoon : the time around or following noon or nones .
